<div class="inner" id="msg_1106164">Character<br>：欧尼加（Onega)/三浦鬼之助（きすけ）（Miura Kisuke）<br>sex：男<br>age:26<br>Concept<br>：黑人武士<br>Nation<br>：扶桑（+1brawn或+1resolve）<br>Religion：The Lwa of Ifri<br>Secret Societies：-<br>Faver:-<br>Reputations：—<br>Wealth：0<br>英雄点：1<br><br>Arcana<br>Virtue：胜利<br>　　当你在战斗中第一次伤害一个恶棍时激活你的Virtue，她除了受到的正常伤害，还额外受到一点戏剧伤害。<br>Hubris：忠诚<br>　　当你的主要角色为一个倒下的战友归来或拒绝留下一个受伤的盟友时，获得一点英雄点。<br><br>Traits：<br>　　体魄(Brawn)：3<br>　　灵巧(Finesse)：4<br>　　决心(Resolve)：2<br>　　机敏(Wits)：2<br>　　风度(Panache)：2<br><br>Skills：肉搏3，瞄准1，军事1，武器3，骑术2，躲藏3，调查1，诱惑1，偷窃1，运动3，学识1<br><br>Rank 3: Re-Roll a single die<br>Rank 4: Sets of 15 = 2 Raises<br>Rank 5: 10s explode (+1 die)<br><br>Death Spiral<br>&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]【】+1 Bonus Die to all Risks<br>&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]【】Villains gain +2 Bonus Dice<br>&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]【】Your 10s explode (+1 die)<br>&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]&#91;]【】You become Helpless<br><br>Backgrounds<br>武士（扶桑）<br>癖好：当你坚持武士信条而导致自己陷入麻烦时获得1英雄点<br>优势：决斗流派（居合道）<br>技能：brawl，aim，warfare，weaponry，ride<br>武士信条：义、勇、仁、礼、诚、名誉、忠义、克己<br><br>仆人&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>　　你为主人工作，无论他的出价是什么。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>癖好：当你把自己置于险地去帮助另一个角色完成一项艰巨的任务时，赚取一点英雄点。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>优势：风雨人生、团队精神&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>技能：躲藏、调查、骑术、诱惑、偷窃<br><br>Advabtages<br>居合道<br>　　流派增益：当你使用武士刀且刀收入鞘内时，你能够用被称为拔刀术的特殊剑术替换Lunge。<br>花费所有Raise，对敌人造成如同所花费的Raise+Finesse+Weaponry的Wound。<br>本剑术能够在所有其他人物行动之前使用。每次战斗只能使用一次。<br><br>风雨人生(FOUL WEATHER JACK)<br>　　你的主要角色获得一个次要故事。你用和创作其他主要角色故事一样的方式创作这个故事，它的发展和奖励都是独立决定的。当这个故事完成后，你可以写一个新的。<br><br>团队精神(TEAM PLAYER)<br>　　当你花费一个成功创造一个机遇时，你就可以花费第二个成功。如果你这样做了，你就代表另一个自愿的主要角色激活这个机遇——她就不需要花费自己的成功了。<br><br>WE SHARE OUR VICTORIES&nbsp; (3 IF JARAGUAN)<br>When you help another Hero complete a Step in his personal Hero Story, you gain a Hero Point. Whenever another Hero helps you complete a Step in your personal Hero Story, he gains a Hero Point.<br><br>HELPING HAND(1point)<br>Activate this Advantage to assist an ally (giving her three Bonus Dice for a Risk) without spending a Hero Point. You can only activate this Advantage once per session.<br><br>大个儿（LARGE）(1point)<br>　　你不能购买【小个儿】优势。<br>　　在任何因为你的体形从而更容易的危机中你都会获得1颗奖励骰——使用运动技能全速奔跑甚至还扛着另一个主要角色或者逼近某人去恐吓他们。<br><br>毒药免疫（POISON IMMUNITY）（2point）<br>　　除了可能有点儿轻微不适，毒药不会影响到你。如果毒药通常会杀死你，它可能只会让你呕吐，但没有其他的效果。<br><br>BODYGUARD（2point）<br>You can spend a Hero Point when an ally would be dealt Wounds. Spend Raises to avoid those Wounds for that ally.<br><br>铁胃（CAST IRON STOMACH）(1point)<br>　　变质或生的食物永远不会给你带来负面影响，你仍然会从中获得所需的营养。<br><br><br>Disadvabtages<br>Obligation 1<br>You promised someone a favor, ranging from something simple and easy to accomplish (delivering a letter) to a highly dangerous or monumental task (betraying your country or a beloved). When the time comes, you must fulfil your promise, whatever the cost. If you fail, you gain a Sworn Enemy whose power equals the Obligation’s cost.<br><br>Sworn Enemy 4<br>A Villain is after you and everything you hold dear. They won’t stop until they destroy you. A minor Villain (Power 5) grants 1 point, whereas a powerful, nation-shaking individual grants 5 points. The points also indicate how often the Villain interferes with the Hero. A minor Villain might appear perhaps once per session, in the background, warning guards, cooperating with the story’s main Bad Guy etc. Selecting a 5-point Sworn Enemy should result in serious trouble, all the time, naturally in addition to the current, story-driven problems. Traitors turning up, brute squads and minor villains hunting the Hero, spies seeing their every move, poisoned food and drink etc.<br><br>Stories<br>Name：返乡<br>Goal：回到故乡<br>Reward：武器4<br>Step 1：从这该死的束缚释放自己！<br>Step 2：<br>Step x：<br>Step x：<br><br>Second Stories<br>Name：救主<br>Goal：将小主公带离扶桑的追击<br>Reward：招牌物品(SIGNATURE ITEM)(3point)<br>Step 1：找到小主公，救他出来<br>Step 2：<br>Step x：<br>Step x：<br><br>物品：<br>武士刀-胧村正（招牌物品）<br><br>Mawon territory<br>主公：松平信广（matsudaira Nobutaka）<br>小主公：松平清佳（Matsudaira Sayaka）</div>
